{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/Sample_A2.gif?t=1738912183\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/newtittle1_e.png?t=1738912183\" />In a remote, peaceful sun-drenched valley lives a tribe of fox people who came here a century ago to escape war. The village chief Banro has a beautiful wife and two pretty young daughters: the elder Oretti and the younger Melanie. One day, a group of vicious slave traders attacks the village, abducting many of its inhabitants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Oretti, captured by the slave traders, is sold into the darkest streets of the royal capital Jerez. Her master is Gulos, the self-proclaimed king of the black market, known for his lustfulness, quick temper, and cruelty, who shows no regard for the lives of his slaves. Here, Oretti meets fellow slave Shanta, who has lost all hope and no longer pursues freedom, as well as Ailofen, known as the Elven Empress of the underground arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Oreti must find a way to survive under Gulos's endless exploitation, overcome the influence of the slave mark magic, and attempt to find allies. She strives to reunite with her family while working with her allies to escape from Gulos's terrifying rule.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/Sample_A3.gif?t=1738912183\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/newtittle2_e.png?t=1738912183\" />A Classic Japanese-style RPG, continuing the gladiator world setting. Players take on the role of the slave Oreti, seeking meaning for survival in the turbulent black market of the royal capital. Besides competing in the illegal underground arena, Oreti must also work in brothels, taverns, and other places to earn money to satisfy Gulos's greed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Through repeated battles and Elofin's training, you will grow step by step. With diverse skill combinations and a character growth system, accumulating strength will be key to breaking free from Gulos's rule!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/Sample_A5.gif?t=1738912183\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/newtittle3_e.png?t=1738912183\" />Stay true to your original intent, believing that one day you'll reunite with your family?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or succumb to lust, completely falling to become Gulos's plaything?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiple endings - how you survive in the black market is entirely up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/Sample_A7.png?t=1738912183\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/newtittle4_e.png?t=1738912183\" />Rather than devouring you whole,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The monsters here prefer to humiliate you with various plays during battle...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/Sample_A6_EN.gif?t=1738912183\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/newtittle5_e.png?t=1738912183\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/Sample_A9.gif?t=1738912183\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2875610/extras/Sample_A8.png?t=1738912183\" />